snippet.title: How The Pogba Bruno Partnership Will Look At Manchester United | A Tactical & Statistical Analysis
snippet.description:
The Premier League is back after a three-month break and Manchester United will have all to play for as the football resumes. With Champions League spots on the line and a chance to win some silverware in the FA Cup and the Europa League, the Red Devils will look to have a strong finish to the season. After Bruno Fernandes' transfer from SP Lisbon in January, the Portuguese has been United's standout performer. But it was unsure to whether United's two talismans in Paul Pogba and Bruno Fernandes will ever share the same pitch at United with Pogba's injury worries and uncertain future. But as he has come back healthy from the break, United fans will have a chance to see them play together in the midfield at Old Trafford. But how will they fit in? What formation & system could Ole Gunnar Solskjaer deploy? Will they complement each other? Watch the video to find out!🔔 SUBSCRIBE here http://bit.ly/1CmczHm

snippet.title: Who is Jude Bellingham? Manchester United's Wonderkid Transfer Target
snippet.description:
The Transfer Rumours of Jude Bellingham signing for Manchester United have received a significant amount of buzz & speculations since January. It looked like Dortmund were the clear frontrunners to sign Bellingham before the season was suspended, but now it looks like Manchester United have overtaken their German Rivals in their pursuit to sign the English Wonderkid. In this video, we've tried to answer some questions like, Who this young sensation named, 'Jude Bellingham' is? Which clubs has he been linked with? What is his style of play? How will he fit in at Manchester United if he signs? And what the future looks like for him.
